The '''Kiris shipyards''' were created sometime around [[30 ABY/Legends|30 ABY]] by [[Thrackan Sal-Solo]] and his supporters, and were being used to create a secret [[Corellian Home Fleet|Corellian fleet]].

During [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo's]] secret visit to the [[Kiris Asteroid Cluster]] at the edge of the [[Corellian system/Legends|Corellian system]], it was discovered that the shipyards contained a fleet large enough to smash the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] blockade in the system. The fleet included three [[Corellian Dreadnaught]]s which included the Corellian [[Flagship/Legends|flagship]], the [[Thrackan Sal-Solo (starship)|''Thrackan Sal-Solo'']].

